FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://retail.oracle.org/

# Retail Products API

Allows clients to query for production information details product/details/{id} 
or product summary /product/summary/{id}


## Product Details [/product/details/{item}]

### Get product details [GET]

+ Parameters
    + item (number) - Product item number.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "item":"946479",
                "name": "Samsung 27 inches Widescreen LED Monitor, Black",
                "Manufacturer": "Samsung",
                "model": "S27E310HS",
                "screen type": "LED",
                "price": "189.99",
                "diagonal screen size": "27 inches",
                "dimensions:": "25.33 H x 18.23 W x 7.90 D",
                "native resolution": "1920 x 1080",
                "contrast ratio": "1,000:1",
                "signal input type": "D-Sub 1",
                "typical response time": "1 ms",
                "aspect ratio": "16:9",
                "Horizontal Viewing Angle": "170/160 degrees"
            }
        ]


